            "title": "長和據報下周不會如期簽約出售巴拿馬港口",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">《南華早報》引述消息指，長和(00001)不會如期下周簽約出售巴拿馬運河兩個港口。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"巴拿馬港口。AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250321_CR_source_ap_panama-hutchison2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"巴拿馬港口。AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250321_CR_source_ap_panama-hutchison2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">巴拿馬港口。AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">接近長和消息人士稱，下周不會正式簽約出售巴拿馬兩個港口。據了解，這情況並不意味著交易被取消，而是因為交易的複雜性，仍有重要細節尚待決定。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14813187-%e9%95%b7%e5%92%8c%e6%93%9a%e5%a0%b1%e4%b8%8b%e5%91%a8%e4%b8%8d%e6%9c%83%e7%b0%bd%e7%b4%84%e5%87%ba%e5%94%ae%e5%b7%b4%e6%8b%bf%e9%a6%ac%e6%b8%af%e5%8f%a3",
